expression.expression-string: "SELECT d.*, ad.appusers_id, ad.grantedDescription, ad.isConfirmed, ad.userDescription, ap.email FROM pjkursdb.discounts d join pjkursdb.appusers_discounts ad on d.id = ad.discount_id join pjkursdb. appusers ap on ad.appusers_id = ap.id where ad.isConfirmed is null"
